Package: PolarGeolocation
Type: Package
Title: R Package: Light-level geolocation analysis tool for data recorded in high latitudes
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Simeon Lisovski
Maintainer: Simeon Lisovski <Simeon.lisovski@gmail.com>
Description: Package specifically created to estimate breeding sites in high 
  Arctic breeding waders carrying a geolocator that measures the full light spectrum. 
  While it is created for this specific purpose the method can be applied to 
  geolocator data in general. Locations are estimated using a template-fit approach.
Depends:
    stats,
    SGAT,
    MASS,
    zoo,
    maptools,
    raster,
    parallel
Suggests:
    TwGeos
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
